  "key": "C major",
  "genre": [
    "Alternative",
    "Indie"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 4,
  "lyrics": "It's got me moving with you, it's got me dreaming of you, oh I'm so in love with you, so in love with you. I hate to see you go, but I love to watch you leave, baby. If you are moving that way, you're moving me right next to you, baby, yeah. Your movement moves me, it's like I'm Harrison, turning off Clapton, man, you're my view tonight. You're my view all night, everywhere, each where you wanna find me, even if you tell me to go, I'm still standing here, cause I am so in love with you. I'm so in love with you, every time you move away, I just can't stop. I'm so in love with everything you do and how you speak and talk away and move. I'm just my mind, it's all in a banana, it's all in design, it's all just the things that we wish we could get back, but I'm saying, baby, let's find it another way, cause I'm so in love with you. I'm so lost in your movement, it moves me anyway. Sometimes I can't sit still and think about the way that we could last, and you said you can't go that far, but I want you to remember how that I'm in front of me. It's like a fairytale, a fantasy in my mind. I'm so in love with you and everything you're doing right in front of me. Drop it down and pop it like you buy it from me, like you're a better project, better VV.",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 25.34000015258789,
      "text": "It's got me moving with you, it's got me dreaming of you, oh I'm so in love with you, so in love",
      "start": 9.34000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 26.600000381469727,
      "text": "with you.",
      "start": 25.34000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 32.2599983215332,
      "text": "I hate to see you go, but I love to watch you leave, baby.",
      "start": 26.600000381469727
    },
    {
      "end": 40.02000045776367,
      "text": "If you are moving that way, you're moving me right next to you, baby, yeah.",
      "start": 33.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 48.63999938964844,
      "text": "Your movement moves me, it's like I'm Harrison, turning off Clapton, man, you're my view tonight.",
      "start": 40.02000045776367
    },
    {
      "end": 59.63999938964844,
      "text": "You're my view all night, everywhere, each where you wanna find me, even if you tell",
      "start": 50.02000045776367
    },
    {
      "end": 73.54000091552734,
      "text": "me to go, I'm still standing here, cause I am so in love with you.",
      "start": 60.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 80.9800033569336,
      "text": "I'm so in love with you, every time you move away, I just can't stop.",
      "start": 73.54000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 90.13999938964844,
      "text": "I'm so in love with everything you do and how you speak and talk away and move.",
      "start": 82.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 98.12000274658203,
      "text": "I'm just my mind, it's all in a banana, it's all in design, it's all just the things that",
      "start": 90.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 108.18000030517578,
      "text": "we wish we could get back, but I'm saying, baby, let's find it another way, cause I'm",
      "start": 98.12000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 113.18000030517578,
      "text": "so in love with you.",
      "start": 108.62000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 121.94000244140625,
      "text": "I'm so lost in your movement, it moves me anyway.",
      "start": 115.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 130.13999938964844,
      "text": "Sometimes I can't sit still and think about the way that we could last, and you said you",
      "start": 121.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 140.05999755859375,
      "text": "can't go that far, but I want you to remember how that I'm in front of me.",
      "start": 130.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 144.05999755859375,
      "text": "It's like a fairytale, a fantasy in my mind.",
      "start": 140.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 154.10000610351562,
      "text": "I'm so in love with you and everything you're doing right in front of me.",
      "start": 145.9199981689453
    },
    {
